Class

An object for storing general toolkit data. The data are stored in the right format in the slot data.

Objects from the Class

Objects can be created by calls of the form new("DLM_general", stock).

Slots

Name:
The name of the data
data:
The data correctly formated

Methods

initialize
signature(.Object = "DLM_general"): ...
plot
signature(x = "DLM_general"): ...
summary
signature(object = "DLM_general"): ...

Examples

newdata<-new('DLM_general')
